--- !u!114 &93793169
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 93793167}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b0bc640e58941354f96071f75744abb9, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  canvasGroup: {fileID: 800934516}
  introText: {fileID: 1508274997}
  hintText: {fileID: 0}
  nextSceneName: Town01
  fadeDuration: 1
  introScreens:
  - text: " Project n\xE0y l\xE0 m\u1ED9t fan-made game l\u1EA5y c\u1EA3m h\u1EE9ng
      t\u1EEB Pok\xE9mon, \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c th\u1EF1c hi\u1EC7n cho m\u1EE5c \u0111\xEDch
      h\u1ECDc t\u1EADp v\xE0 th\u1EF1c h\xE0nh ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n game. Ph\xE1t
      tri\u1EC3n b\u1EDFi Tr\u1EA7n V\u0103n Nam (Email: tvnamtv21@gmail.com).\n\n
      Tr\xF2 ch\u01A1i kh\xF4ng c\xF3 li\xEAn h\u1EC7, t\xE0i tr\u1EE3, hay x\xE1c
      nh\u1EADn ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c t\u1EEB Nintendo, Game Freak, Creatures Inc.,
      The Pok\xE9mon Company, hay b\u1EA5t k\u1EF3 \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB s\u1EDF
      h\u1EEFu b\u1EA3n quy\u1EC1n n\xE0o.\n\n To\xE0n b\u1ED9 t\xEAn ri\xEAng, nh\xE2n
      v\u1EADt, h\xECnh \u1EA3nh v\xE0 th\u01B0\u01A1ng hi\u1EC7u Pok\xE9mon thu\u1ED9c
      v\u1EC1 ch\u1EE7 s\u1EDF h\u1EEFu t\u01B0\u01A1ng \u1EE9ng. D\u1EF1 \xE1n n\xE0y
      kh\xF4ng nh\u1EB1m m\u1EE5c \u0111\xEDch th\u01B0\u01A1ng m\u1EA1i."
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    requireZToAdvance: 1
  - text: "\u0110i\u1EC1u khi\u1EC3n di chuy\u1EC3n b\u1EB1ng c\xE1c ph\xEDm m\u0169i
      t\xEAn, z \u0111\u1EC3 x\xE1c nh\u1EADn, x \u0111\u1EC3 t\u1EEB ch\u1ED1i.\n\nNgo\xE0i
      map c\xF3 th\u1EC3 b\u1EA5m x \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF menu.\n\n\u0110\u1EC3 \u0111i
      v\xE0o nh\xE0 c\u1EA7n b\u1EA5m z khi ti\u1EBFp x\xFAc v\u1EDBi c\u1EEDa.\n\n\u0110i
      tr\xEAn c\u1ECF cao, c\xF3 x\xE1c su\u1EA5t g\u1EB7p pokemon hoang d\xE3, c\xF3
      th\u1EC3 b\u1EAFt pokemon hoang d\xE3 (m\xE1u pokemon hoang d\xE3 c\xE0ng \xEDt,
      t\u1EC9 l\u1EC7 b\u1EAFt tr\xFAng c\xE0ng cao)"
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    requireZToAdvance: 1
  - text: "\nN\u1EBFu th\u1EA5y kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt ph\u1EA3i l\xE0m g\xEC ti\u1EBFp
      theo c\xF3 th\u1EC3 m\u1EDF menu (b\u1EA5m x) -> pokemonDex -> m\u0169i t\xEAn
      ph\u1EA3i \u0111\u1EC3 m\u1EDF main story.\n\nT\u01B0\u01A1ng t\u1EF1 pokemonDEX
      -> m\u0169i t\xEAn ph\u1EA3i 2 l\u1EA7n \u0111\u1EC3 xem tutorial"
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    requireZToAdvance: 1
